{"tid":797043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊名校訓導主任 今日有個男學生考試出貓","createTime":"2018-08-28T08:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T16:55:55.000Z","uid":146505,"like":2699,"dislike":242,"uniUserReply":156,"replies":[{"pid":"914cf84073814191f8ca467896efac33ddbeda0b","tid":797043,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"咁循例都要見一見佢家長<br />\n點知佢話自己冇監護人<br />\n心諗佢屋企情況都應該幾複雜<br />\n<br />\n咁就check翻佢入學啲record啦<br />\n點知check到佢爸爸係我地學校個校工<br />\n佢同佢爸爸竟然仲唔同姓氏 追問下竟然發現個男仔自己去改咗個姓氏<br />\n要父子家庭關係幾惡劣先會令自己個仔改走個姓氏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個校工叔叔平時都奇奇怪怪 好似仲經常手震 似係有啲怪病<br />\n咁anyway都通知翻佢啦 希望可以合作教翻乖個小朋友<br />\n<br />\n點知同佢爸爸講多兩講 佢知道佢個仔考試出貓<br />\n佢爸爸竟然出手毆打佢<br />\n好似當佢係仇人咁打 成張木凳車埋去<br />\n嚇死我同其他老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難想像個男仔喺咁惡劣嘅家教環境底下長大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話窮等人家生仔 仲要單親家庭真係唔會有好嘅教育<br />\n難怪個男仔會出貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身為訓導主任有咩方法可以幫到呢兩父子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c42b3c31349fd1e60ff3869ee63293cef96a95","tid":797043,"uid":199211,"like":35,"dislike":676,"score":-641,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"起完底知咩事"},{"pid":"2ae3a4c41e73190b8de6da2702e8b2808e396338","tid":797043,"uid":14065,"like":770,"dislike":17,"score":753,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"悶啦"},{"pid":"0a569f9cb2d5b6bb6df94fcaf9efb8638545ed99","tid":797043,"uid":20241,"like":27,"dislike":412,"score":-385,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:12:36.000Z","msg":"名校點解會收呢啲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1235d6fdebed5c4c938dee4d1b062e808dae2bc8","tid":797043,"uid":28743,"like":1056,"dislike":4,"score":1052,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"你係秦沛？