s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身為訓導主任有咩方法可以幫到呢兩父子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"未夠十八，冇父母同意點改姓名？"},{"pid":"7fdbdce3a0ef1a45685a992b4af1eb0f642f1f20","tid":797043,"uid":90244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"去少d 馬場啦你"},{"pid":"2d0e6948aa25049966c50d0433a1a5e60fa56c12","tid":797043,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"樓豬之前賭輸左比個學生仲屈人出千<br />\n<br />\n依家條氣唔順又想屈人出貓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a0d715f1261118c375ada789627a7b832f39a9","tid":797043,"uid":124585,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:32:33.000Z","msg":"一個姓周, 一個姓曹. 竟然係父子關係？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f2ec38d932dd427baf4679743515524519c690","tid":797043,"uid":92017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"出貓唔啱嘅，出貓啱好呀嘛，出貓唔好呀老師下，出貓...無咩我地返出去喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a5c81d03a057fdd9c31fda6f83f9b4e592ed80","tid":797043,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1235d6fdebed5c4c938dee4d1b062e808dae2bc8","tid":797043,"uid":28743,"like":1056,"dislike":4,"score":1052,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"你係秦沛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"你大～我呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7e2b7aad808f7613d7c0aa20f515b637bbcc45","tid":797043,"uid":133714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"善良的槍開唔到<br />\n記住要丟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50386db875a11afaf804702f1f74c10e7a497a62","tid":797043,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit